long_description:
stacked exports inc is an export brokerage and forwarding service, based in osaka japan. before we recently changed our name to better reflect our services. stacked exports inc is a licenced and registered car dealer and car exporter in osaka japan. since our name change, we have undergone a major restructuring to build a more efficient system to meet our growing customers' needs. the more parts our clients sell, the more they order. the more money you make, the more money we make, it's team work. we are a wholesale exporter based in osaka japan. although we specialize in vehicles and parts, we can export anything you want. stacked gets its name because we take pride in "stacking" parts and vehicles into containers. 
if you are interested, then please contact us. stacked exports inc is a wholesale import / export agent and forwarding service based in osaka japan. we assist our clients in sourcing, purchasing, receiving, storage and export.
